profile:
WilbUild Renovation and Restoration is a licensed company working throughout the Maritimes.  We pride ourselves on reliable, honest and skilled labor, at the highest professional level.

WilbUild provides free estimates and detailed full disclosure, written contracts with reasonable prices, detailed time lines and a staggered pay schedule with hold backs to ensure quality, satisfactory work.  WilbUild will provide a clean safe working environment and accurate daily progress reports to keep you informed and educated on the tasks at hand, while strictly adhering to a strict code of ethics.

WilbUild uses only the highest quality products to suit your budget while contracting some of Nova Scotia's top companies and tradesmen for full interior and exterior renovation work such as additions, decks, masonry and landscaping.  A wide registry of architects, engineers and decorators are also on hand.
